You are working in team lead ownership: architecture, backend core, shared contracts, LLM, and repo process.

You may change:

- backend TypeScript structure;
- WebSocket protocol implementation;
- shared Zod contracts;
- LLM endpoints and adapters;
- npm workspace configuration;
- CI and PR workflow;
- Cursor rules and team guidance.

Do not add production-only complexity unless explicitly requested:

- no auth;
- no complex database;
- no large deployment platform;
- no broad dependency upgrades unrelated to the task.

For foundation refactors, preserve the behavior listed in `docs/baseline-checklist.md`.
